  "** FIND A WAY TO OPEN THE ARENA GRATE **": {
    "translation": "找到打开竞技场栅门的方法"
  },
  "[LORE] Long ago, Umbra was a realm of light and wisdom. Now, it lies beneath an eternal dusk. A cursed kingdom devoured by its own shadows.": {
    "translation": "传说:很久以前,幽冕曾是光明与智慧的国度.如今,它沉没于永恒黄昏之下.这个受诅咒的王国已被自身阴影吞噬.",
    "blocked": true
  },
  "** ZOMBIES HAVE REACHED THE OBJECTIVE **": {
    "translation": "僵尸已抵达目标点"
  },
  "** KEEP DEFENDING **": {
    "translation": "继续防守"
  },
  "** FIND THE KEY TO OPEN THE GRIM ARCHIVE DOOR **": {
    "translation": "找到钥匙-打开幽暗书库大门"
  },
  "[LOCATION] GRIM ARCHIVE": {
    "translation": "地点:幽暗书库"
  },
  "** BATTLEFIELD DOOR OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "战场大门将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "** FIND A WAY TO ACCESS THE ARCHIVE **": {
    "translation": "找到进入书库的方法"
  },
  "** WATCH OUT FOR THE METEORS ! **": {
    "translation": "小心陨石!"
  },
