    "translation": "电梯将在20秒后离开"
  },
  "** ACTIVATE 3 LEVERS TO OPEN BOTH PATH **": {
    "translation": "启动3个拉杆以开启两条道路"
  },
  "** DOORS OPENING IN 15 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "大门将在15秒后开启"
  },
  "** BASTION EXIT GATE OPENING IN 15 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "堡垒出口大门将在15秒后开启"
  },
  "[LOCATION] SIEGEBOUND COURT": {
    "translation": "地点:围城王庭"
  },
  "[LORE] Once a place of strategy and might, now abandoned, the court trembles under the weight of forgotten wars.": {
    "translation": "传说:这里曾是谋略与武力之地,如今已被遗弃,王庭在被遗忘战争的重压下颤动.",
    "blocked": true
  },
  "** DOOR OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "大门将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "** BASTION ENTRANCES OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "堡垒入口将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "[LORE] Shadows coil along the ramparts, hiding the secrets of a kingdom long devoured by darkness.": {
    "translation": "传说:阴影盘绕在城墙之上,掩藏着一个早已被黑暗吞噬的王国秘辛.",
    "blocked": true
  },
  "** SPLIT ON BOTH SIDES **": {
    "translation": "两侧分开行动"
  },
  "** GRIM ARCHIVE ARENA GRATE OPENING IN 20 SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "幽暗书库竞技场栅门将在20秒后开启"
  },
  "** GET INSIDE THE GRIM ARCHIVE ARENA AND KEEP DEFENDING **": {
    "translation": "进入幽暗书库竞技场并继续防守"
  },
  "[LORE] Echoes of the Grim Archive awaken something ancient, a protector forged from memory and bone.": {
    "translation": "传说:幽暗书库的回响唤醒了某个古老存在,那是由记忆与骸骨锻成的守护者.",
