  },
  "** RESIST 20 MORE SECONDS **": {
    "translation": "再坚持20秒"
  },
  "[LORE] Echoes of the past linger here, whispers of scholars lost to the darkness that consumes this place.": {
    "translation": "传说:过往的回声仍滞留于此,那是学者们被吞噬此地的黑暗吞没前留下的低语.",
